COLLABORATIVE EVOLUTION:
The Matrix Protocol is designed for open, collaborative evolution. Any improvements, 
extensions, or modifications to the core Protocol concepts should be proposed 
through the official channels at https://matrix-protocol.org to benefit the entire 
community.

